    public abstract class AbstractCRUDController<T extends AbstractModel,PK extends java.io.Serializable>
extends play.mvc.Controller
    Abstract class represents a CRUD Controller with the most necessary methods. Create, update, get (read), get all (read all) and a generic query method find. The class contains a GenericDAO with the parameters T (Model Class) and PK (Private Key). Class is annotated with Singleton which advises the DI framework to instantiate the class only once.
    Author:
    cbi
